0.8934, 100.6311, 101.5057, 101.6215, 101.8191, 101.1743, 101.2072, 100.8078, 101.4195, 101.8267, 102.0072, 102.0744, 104.2058, 103.2648, 103.341, 102.9218, 103.5292, 103.8432, 102.8818, 101.4976, 102.68, 102.9536, 103.0857, 103.1797, 103.4566, 105.2923, 103.2423, 102.7354, 104.0085, 103.1277, 102.7293, 103.719, 104.9918, 105.216, 104.9464, 105.519, 105.4996, 104.8464, 104.3872, 105.1593, 106.9772, 105.9385, 105.7831, 108.8191, 108.3846, 108.2875, 109.2331, 109.843, 110.2968, 110.1557, 109.5625, 109.4259, 110.1353, 110.8939, 111.1143, 112.2004, 114.0806, 114.3051, 115.3054, 115.2739, 114.8742, 114.3515, 114.8376, 114.0869, 114.4733, 114.216, 112.5936, 111.995, 111.3541, 111.8265, 112.1989, 113.7136, 113.1611, 112.4904, 112.0661, 112.2702, 113.18, 116.248, 117.0684, 117.8265, 116.8827, 117.0921, 118.17, 118.2451, 119.1554, 119.6031, 118.7626, 118.4308, 118.9977, 119.4662, 119.716, 119.737, 119.2231, 119.7625, 120.3954, 120.9108, 119.5197, 119.3794, 119.6525, 119.6042, 120.175, 121.302, 121.8762, 122.618, 122.3017, 121.6155, 122.1557, 122.2838, 122.4557, 122.6647, 122.0563, 121.8961, 122.3956, 121.1704, 120.8791, 121.2479, 121.0279, 122.0534, 122.8439, 124.0585, 122.9148, 123.2424, 124.5364, 125.7369, 126.1797, 124.4316, 123.7652, 124.1674, 123.057, 125.3566, 125.3878, 124.0835, 123.3952, 124.6986, 123.118, 123.653, 123.0611, 121.875, 122.6739, 121.9005, 121.4538, 122.553, 122.0581, 124.1556, 124.3937, 123.9322, 125.1844, 124.1689, 124.3861, 125.4575, 125.6106, 125.0095, 124.4707, 123.9946, 124.5903, 122.5884, 123.2008, 123.0299, 124.5543, 123.3341, 122.9452, 123.504, 124.2749, 122.3625, 122.477, 121.033, 121.2219, 121.6778, 121.5718, 119.8471, 121.0199, 121.6619, 120.3255, 118.8918, 119.726, 118.2408, 117.8385, 115.4001, 116.3406, 115.9504, 114.6184, 115.9123, 116.9754, 116.8526, 118.0135, 118.6799, 117.4573, 116.4694, 117.7478], "summary_html": "<h1>CFTC头寸截面因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 0.97)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报基于CFTC披露的COT数据，按投资者类型（生产贸易商、互换交易商、资金管理者、散户）构造截面因子：生产贸易商/互换交易商净多头较多的品种未来收益较高，散户净多头较多的品种未来收益较低。由于国内缺乏分投资者类型数据，本复现使用 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20名席位净持仓差）作为代理变量，正值代表机构净多头占优（类似生产贸易商正向信号）。最优变体为短窗口滚动分位数 + 扩张窗口分位数的双因子组合，通过截面排名做多空，捕捉机构持仓对商品收益的截面预测力。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-3.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1731</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.04</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.39</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.95 / 1.14</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.81</td><td>0.42</td><td>1.67</td><td>0.87</td><td>1.25</td><td>1.43</td><td>1.56</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.46</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 25 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 25 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1730</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>49.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>净持仓滚动分位数（核心因子）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{(S,W)} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}{\\max_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}</div>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">m_t</span>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">S</span>: MA平滑窗口 (最优 S=20)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span>: 滚动分位数窗口 (最优 W=65 日)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>扩张窗口分位数</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{exp} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}{\\max_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo} = 0.6 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{(20,65)}) + 0.4 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{exp})</div>\n<p>截面排名后映射到 [-1, 1] 连续信号，经 vol_target_scale 波动率缩放，每 25 日换仓。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.62, backtest未通过。单因子+短hold, S=5/10效果差</td><td>全因子实现: 分位数/情绪/变化/扩张, grid覆盖MA(5/10/20)+窗口+hold</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;识别S=20+W=65为最优</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Sharpe 0.94, 通过。S=20明显最优, CS归一化大幅提升, H25&gt;H10</td><td>扩大S=20 grid, 加IC-gated, 加combo(q65+chg20和q130+sent65)</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;0.94, best=nq_s20_w65_H25_cs</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>Sharpe 0.94已通过, 可继续优化。combo可进一步提升</td><td>聚焦S=20, 新增W=50, 加H30, 扩张分位数改用MA20, 新增combo(q65+expanding), 三因子组合</td><td>Sharpe 0.94-&gt;0.97, best=combo_q65exp_H25_cs</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2发现MA20平滑远优于MA5/10 (信号更稳定, 减少噪声交易); R3将扩张窗口分位数改为基于MA20计算(与最优单因子一致), 并将其与短窗口分位数组合, 利用\"当前水平 vs 短期区间\"和\"当前水平 vs 全历史区间\"两个互补视角, 进一步提升Sharpe至0.97。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差, 非空率约23%)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种 (57个有效品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 25日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>信号方向</strong>: 做多机构净多头品种, 做空机构净空头品种</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: (1) memberdiff20仅覆盖前20大席位, 非空率约23%, 部分品种/日期缺失; (2) 国内席位持仓与CFTC分类不完全对应, 但核心逻辑一致(机构持仓正向预测); (3) 最大回撤约50%, 受CS归一化放大影响; (4) 2025年初yearly Sharpe接近0, 近期效果偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MA_SMOOTH</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>MA smoothing window for memberdiff20</td></tr><tr><td><code>MA_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>min_periods for MA</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>65</code></td><td>rolling quantile window for npos_q_s20_w65</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>min_periods for rolling min/max (max(20, W//4))</td></tr><tr><td><code>COMBO_WEIGHTS</code></td><td><code>[0.6, 0.4]</code></td><td>weights: [npos_q_s20_w65, sent_expanding]</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.2s</li>\n</ul>"}